  <summary>3/23/2000--Introduced.
Child Support Fairness and Tax Refund Interception Act of 2000 - Amends title IV part D (Child Support and Establishment of Paternity) of the Social Security Act to provide for the use of the tax refund intercept program to collect past-due child support on behalf of children who are not minors.</summary>
